name: yodatools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.2.0a0" %}

package:
  name: yodatools
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/Y/YODA-Tools/YODA-Tools-0.2.0a0.tar.gz
  sha256: 8b370029b945da34d093865f221ac734570f97906f598cbd21ff1ef1e94919f9

build:
  number: 1000
  skip: True  # [py3k]
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .
  entry_points:
    - yodatools = yodatools.dataloader.controller.Main:main

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - odm2api
    - openpyxl
    - pandas
    - pyyaml
    - wxpython ==3.0.0.0
    - xlrd

test:
  imports:
    - yodatools

about:
  home: https://github.com/ODM2/YODA-Tools
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: 'Tools to validate and manage YODA files'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - emiliom
    - lsetiawan
    - ocefpaf
